# Documentação

## Criação de serviço

```
sudo vi /etc/systemd/system/guerraacademy.service

```

* Conteúdo do serviço:
```
[Unit]
Description=Guerra Academy Backend
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/opt/landing-backend/guerraacademy
WorkingDirectory=/opt/landing-backend
Restart=always
User=root

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
```


```
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl start guerraacademy
sudo systemctl status guerraacademy
sudo systemctl stop guerraacademy
sudo systemctl restart guerraacademy
sudo systemctl enable guerraacademy
```

